Complete Color Schema for Lifecycle Statuses
1. WAITING_PAYMENT (Blue)
Badge: bg-blue-100 text-blue-700 border-blue-200
Gradient: from-blue-200/70 via-blue-100/50 to-blue-200/70
Background: bg-blue-50 border-blue-300
Icon Background: bg-blue-500
Blur Effects (light): bg-blue-200/40
Blur Effects (dark): bg-blue-300/40
AI Recommendations Card: border-2 border-blue-300 bg-gradient-to-br from-blue-50 to-cyan-50
AI Recommendations Icon: text-blue-600
AI Recommendations Title: text-blue-700
Recommendation Items: bg-white border-blue-300, bg-blue-500, text-blue-900, text-blue-800
Button: bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-600 to-cyan-600 hover:from-blue-700 hover:to-cyan-700

