Note: VISIBLE uses full emerald green, while HIDDEN uses teal (emerald with a gray-blue mix) to maintain similarity with distinction. FLAGGED and BLOCKED use amber and red respectively, with consistent color application across badges, timelines, and AI recommendations sections.